#example turn on your heatpump at lowest cost

this example uses minimal coding

##1. create the helpers
> goto settings>devices & services > Helpers
> create Helper (right bottom)
> select date and/or time
> the name I used 'starttime heatpump'
> select 'Date and time'
> create Helper (right bottom)
> select date and/or time
> the name I used 'endtime heatpump'
> select 'Date and time'

##2. create automation to calculate start and end time

##3. create automation to switch the heatpump
